This directory stores runtime patent data artifacts. Do not commit actual data files.

Directory structure:
  data/
    raw/
      patentsview/        — RawPatentsViewRecord JSON files, keyed by patentId
      maintenance-fees/   — RawMaintenanceFeeRecord JSON files, keyed by patentId
      patent-center/      — RawPatentCenterRecord JSON files, keyed by patentId
    merged/
      {patentId}.json     — Final merged Partial<PatentRecord> per patent

All files are written atomically (write to .tmp.json, then rename).
Each file includes a _fetchedAt ISO timestamp for traceability.
